---
title: Smart Rosemary Pork Chops with Apricot-Mustard Vinaigrette, Apples and Roasted Broccoli
description: Tonight's hearty salad with apples and roasted broccoli are dressed with an apricot and mustard vinaigrette and topped with rosemary-coated pork chops  A sprinkling of crunchy seeds completes a hearty salad that's perfect for any time of the year!
